Dialogs.Dialog: You know... Rinko is cooking dinner tonight, so why don't you come over to my house to eat？ If you can't don't worry.
Don't say that, of course I'm going.
Really？ Hehe... then, I'll go home first after school and wait for you, so come over anytime.
Hehe... I knew you would say that. Okay, I'll get ready, I'll see you later.
I'm a little bit out of the loop today... Sorry.
Maybe this is the first time you've had dinner at Rinko's house？
That's right. I'm a little nervous.
It's not the first time. Come on. You can make yourself comfortable.
Today, I wanted you to try a dish I recently learned to cook. Well, I'll let you enjoy it when it's ready.
In the meantime, I have a menu in mind, but if you want something else to eat... just let me know, okay？
Okay. Then, I'll try to cook a dish I've recently learned.
Okay. Since it's special, I'll make you something you'll like.
I'd like to request this: ▲メニュー▲.
Sorry to keep you waiting. I feel like I did a pretty good job, so here's hoping for the best.
Sorry for the wait. Well, try it.
Sorry, I made you wait. I might have messed up a little... But don't worry, it's edible.
I'm trying something new. What do you think？
I'm putting my own twist on it this time.
I tried a Rinko-style arrangement today, hehe.
Following a recipe if fine, but I think you're own when you can bring out your individuality. What do you think？
Today's dish is a little more creative. I wonder if you can tell the difference.
I'm a little particular about the seasoning on this one. Do you think it will suit you palate？
I'm confident about my Japanese food, you know. Well, if you eat it, you'll understand.
I think I'm best at Japanese food these days. I don't know if it matches your taste, though.
I've been enjoying a good taste of Japanese food lately.
Western food is a broad category, but I think Rinko is rather good at it.
I've been feeling confident about making Western food lately.
Leave it to me to season Western food. I'm sure it will suit your palate as well.
I'm pretty proud that I can cook Chinese food well.
Rinko is pretty good at Chinese food. Well, why don't you try it？ I won't let you say I'm bragging about it, hehe.
Lately, when I make Chinese food, the flavor and the oil level are just right. Do I have good taste？
I've gotten really good at this kind of cooking lately. I think I have good taste, don't you？
What do you think about a girlfriend who is good at this kind of cooking？ Hehe.
I've been getting good at cooking like this lately. I'm sure you'll say it's delicious, too.
With Rinko, any dish is perfect.
Lately, whatever I cook goes well. I'm sure today's will be delicious too.
Does Rinko have a good taste in cooking？ I feel like saying I'm good at all the dishes... Hehe.
I feel like... Japanese food is so hard to make. I'm trying my best to make it, but... what am I missing？
Hah... Japanese food is a delicate dish. I tried my best in Rinko's way... you should try it.
I haven't been able to prepare Japanese food well lately... I've been working pretty hard on it though.
You know... I haven't been able to make Western food well lately. But I worked really hard on this, okay？
Western food looks simple, but it's very deep. I think today's dish... probably tastes as good as I tried to make it.
I've been having trouble with Western food lately. And today's food, you know, just know that I worked really hard on it, okay？
It's hard to remember the setup for Chinese food... Ah, but there's a lot of love involved in every step of the process.
Chinese seasoning can be unique, right？ So even if this seasoning's unique... it's not Rinko's fault... isn't it？
Chinese food is... hmmm, it was still difficult.
I had a hard time making this dish... But I worked pretty hard on it！
I didn't cut any corners on this. In fact, I put more effort into it than usual...
I tried to make this, but... I'm not too sure about this dish.
These days... I've been having trouble deciding what to make. How can I make it to your liking？
I'm not confident about cooking... I wish they would invent some kind of seasoning that anyone can make delicious food with.
Why cooking has to be so difficult... But you'll eat it because I worked so hard on it, right？
Do you recognize this tableware？ They're the matching ones you gave me, hehe.
I like this tableware. Not because they match, but... because I like them.
Ah, I'm so full. Thanks for the food！
(What is this... I have a strange feeling something is about to happen.)
So, how did you like it？ I'm rather confident in myself.
Well, what do you think？ I'm confident about today's, hehe.
Hey, can you tell me your thoughts？ I'm feeling confident today.
So, how did you like it？
How was it？ Was it good？
Hey, can you tell me your thoughts？
...How was it？ I knew it wouldn't taste good.
(As expected, I think you messed up...)
...What do you think？ If you don't want to say it, that's fine.
This makes it hard to say what you think... right？
Really？ Yay！ Rinko worked really hard. Hehe♪
Really？ That's good. I had a fair amount of confidence.
Huh, really？ ...I thought I definitely failed. Maybe I'm out of sync.
I see. Well then, I guess I've passed the test.
It was good in its own way.
Well, it was just plain delicious.
Really？ Even that one is okay... Hehe.
I guess it wasn't up to my taste.
Huh... I see. I though I did well, but... I guess I need to rethink.
I think I would prefer a different kind of seasoning.
Really？ Well, I'll learn something different next time.
It's just... I don't think it's up to my liking.
...I see. I kind of knew that. I'll try to make it a little better next time.
I want to ask... Should there be days when you don't have a bento？
I hope it's not too hard for you, but I really like the bentos you prepare, ▲小早川＊▲.
Really？ Well then, I will make them again.
I think it's hard on you. It'd be a good idea to go to the cafeteria, ▲小早川＊▲.
I see. Well, Rinko doesn't mind... but it might be fun to go to the school cafeteria.
What do you usually do for breakfast？
I think... I just do what I can.
Well then, how about I go make it for you next time？ If you don't want to, I won't force you to.
How was breakfast the other day？ If you want... I can go and make it again.
It would be helpful if you could prepare breakfast for me.
I want to make my own breakfast...
What... I see. Well, I don't mind.
I've been into baking lately. Would you like to try some？
Of course I want to try.
Hehe... Okay. I'll make it for you next time.
Hey... can I go make dinner again？
If you don't mind, I'd appreciate it if you come to prepare me dinner, ▲小早川＊▲.
Understood. I'll go make it next time, so please look forward to it.
I'd like to make it myself as much as possible...
